<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1227937>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39–42. Phasmatocoris spectrum, male holotype deposited in SDEI. 39, lateral view; 40, labels; 41, genitalia portions and a foreleg glued to a card pinned with the specimen; 42, portion of theleg glued to the paper board,arrows point to the dorsal excavation of the fore tibiae and stiff setae onit." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1227937/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1227927>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21–24. Phasmatocoris papei sp. nov., male genitalia, scale bar 0.2 mm. 21, pygophore, apical half, ventral view; 22, pygophoreand parameres, posterior view; 23–24, right paramere; 23, inner surface; 24, outer surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1227927/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1227925>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–20. Phasmatocoris papei sp. nov., male. 15–16, dorsal view; 15, hind wing, scale bar 1.0 mm; 16, abdominal segments IV(exceptbasal portion)—VII, scalebar 2.0 mm;17–20, scalebar 0.5 mm; 17–19, pygophore and parameres;17–18, lateral view; 18–19, parameres somewhat moved apart; 19, ventral view; 20, pygophore without parameres, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1227925/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1227915>
    dc:description "FIGURES1–5. Phasmatocorispapei sp. nov. 1–2, male holotype; 1, lateral view, scale bar 5.0 mm; 2–3, dorsal view, scalebar 1.0 mm; 2, head and pronotum; 3–5, male paratype; 3, head and fore lobe of pronotum; 4–5, lateral view, scale bar 0.5 mm; 4, head (antenna omitted) and anterior portion of fore lobe of pronotum; 5, thorax, midportion (wings moved down), sct, scutellum, sm, spine of metanotum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1227915/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1227921>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–14. Phasmatocoris papei sp. nov., male, dorsal view. 11–12, scale bar 1.0 mm; 11, holotype, forewing and abdomen, except basal portion; 12, paratype, forewing; 13–14, portion of forewing where the apex of subbasal cell and base of discal cell are more proximate (pointed by an arrow), sb, subbasal cell, bc, basal cell, dc, discal cell, scale bar 0.5 mm; 13, holotype; 14, paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1227921/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

